40|$|Diploma thesis Business {{risks in}} {{insurance}} and their quantification describes the business risks to which {{insurance companies are}} exposed in their activities. Thesis is focused on <b>market</b> <b>risk</b> and quantification of <b>market</b> <b>risk</b> in insurance companies. It includes determination of the specifications for the activities of insurance companies, regulation and characteric of business risks in insurance. Large part of the thesis deals with the method of Value at Risk {{as a tool to}} measure <b>market</b> <b>risk</b> as well as individual methods to calculate it. In the conclusion, thesis describes the processes of quantification of <b>market</b> <b>risk</b> in Generali PPF Holding and in Česká poisťovňa, which gives a practical insight into the issues of <b>market</b> <b>risk</b> in insurance companies...|$|R
